              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/16725881/" class="">入青海</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/ziyouwutongshu/" class=" " title="自由梧桐树">自由梧桐树</a>
                (话好说，事难做。)
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
